íŸ@62b2f8c199a6473f2c30221fa4d53f47526c6ade942d276ab193e7d5c8e8c7a2⁄˚Title: title: bits shl
Path: Examples
Content:
Shift left a number by 7 bits
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 2 | bits shl 7
0

```
Shift left a number with 2 byte by 7 bits
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 2 | bits shl 7 --number-bytes 2
256

```
Shift left a signed number by 1 bit
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x7F | bits shl 1 --signed
-2

```
Shift left a list of numbers
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [5 3 2] | bits shl 2
‚ï≠‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚î¨‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚ïÆ
‚îÇ 0 ‚îÇ 20 ‚îÇ
‚îÇ 1 ‚îÇ 12 ‚îÇ
‚îÇ 2 ‚îÇ  8 ‚îÇ
‚ï∞‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚î¥‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚ïØ


```
Shift left a binary value
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[4f f4] | bits shl 4
Length: 2 (0x2) bytes | null_char printable whitespace ascii_other non_ascii
00000000:   ff 40                                                √ó@


```
